OOC: Continuing where I left off yesterday ...

Rogue Star - Command Center::

"You hit them hard, but not hard enough," Gatara comments.  "They've 
managed to regain control."

"I'm not finished with them yet!" Noir sneers, launching another 
missile volley at the battered target.

<><><><>

Vindicator - Bridge::

Bluestreak screams as his console is blown up by the energy overload 
from the second wave of missile detonations.  Outback pulls his 
injured comrade away, but the damage has been done.  Most of the 
ship's systems are now offline, and it begins the long plunge toward 
the mountains on the northern continent.
